text: Mamdooh Al-Doseri (born 4 August 1971) is a Bahraini former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Bahraini male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Bahrain Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
